Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Mayor Feinstein to stay
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043x04z
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 May 1983
San Francisco mayor Diane Feinstein holds on to her post after handgun row ends in vote. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less